Chula_Vista.Southwestern College (California):
Southwestern College is a public, two-year community college located in the city of Chula Vista, California. Founded in 1961, Southwestern College serves approximately 19,000 students annually.


== History ==
The Southwestern Community College District, located south of San Diego and extending to the U.S.—Mexico border, is one of 72 community college districts in the California Community College system.
